            "id": 74483,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Conclua a chamada da função codificando seu nome.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"displayCash\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" money = \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" currency = \" /><text value=\"&quot; Euros&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(money + currency);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"displayCash();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"107\" endIndex=\"118\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"100 Euros\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>displayCash</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Braces",
            "id": 74532,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O que este código exibe no console?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"daysAYear\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"365\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"daysAYear();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Days a year&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"365\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Days a year\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>365</code> em uma linha e <code>Days a year</code> na próxima</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>365</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\"><code>Days a year</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>365</code> em uma linha e <code>Days a year</code> na próxima.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Pass parameters",
            "id": 74639,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Qual é o parâmetro nesta função?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"addUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"user\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" text = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Added: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(text + user);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>user</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>text</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\">Não há parâmetro</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>user</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
